author: wsjcom
title: Trump to Visit the United Kingdom on July 13
text:
2 COMMENTS WASHINGTON—President Donald Trump is scheduled to visit the U.K. on July 13, the White House said Thursday, and he is expected to meet U.K. Prime Minister Theresa May.
In January, President Trump canceled a planned trip to the U.K. —long intended to be his first official visit to the country—in an indication of how frosty relations between the U.K and the U.S. had become.
